7 (4 nights)\\n- Sunny Shore B&B, Dar es Salaam — Aug 17–19 (2 nights)\\n- Ramses Hilton, Cairo — Aug 19–20 (1 night)\\n\\nSAFARI (Suricata Safaris Ltd):\\n- 3-day group camping safari, Aug 7–9.\\n- Tarangire NP → Lake Manyara NP → Ngorongoro Crater.\\n- Contact: Richard, +255 763 222 293, info@suricatasafaris.com\\n- Cost: $1,200 total for 2 pax. $240 deposit paid (20%). $960 balance due on arrival.\\n- Payment: cash (USD post-2009 notes) or Pesapal online (+5% surcharge): payments.pesapal.com/suricatasafaris\\n- Ngorongoro nights are cold — warm layers essential.\\n- August is peak season with Great Wildebeest Migration.\\n\\nDINING:\\n- The Rock Restaurant, Zanzibar — Aug 15, 18:00–20:00, 2 adults. Fully paid ($46). Outdoor seating requested.\\n- 2x Tropical Passion Fruit Cheesecake included.\\n- Contact: +255 776 591 360 / +255 763 070 658, booking@therockrestaurantzanzibar.com\\n\\nCAIRO SIGHTSEEING:\\n- Stopover 1 (Aug 3–4): Grand Egyptian Museum, Pyramids of Giza. Eileen Hotel base.\\n- Stopover 2 (Aug 19–20): Islamic Cairo, the Citadel, Khan el-Khalili bazaar, Coptic Cairo. Ramses Hilton base.\\n\\nZANZIBAR:\\n- Driving: IDP + local Zanzibar Driving Permit (~$15, valid up to 3 months). Carry both; police checkpoints frequent.\\n- Swimming: north coast (Nungwi ar\n\n### 123 statement delegate:system-files/dispatch/(model-driven)\n{\"ts\":1784049241950,\"type\":\"statement\",\"context\":\"delegate:system-files/dispatch/(model-driven)\",\"nodeId\":\"delegate_2_b75766a4\",\"code\":\"// The inspect didn't return properly. Let me try a different approach — use display to see the full text, and also display the sheet answer. Then combine and resolve.\\ndisplay(<Stack gap={2}>\\n  <Heading level={2}>Reader Answer (Markdown + PDF)</Heading>\\n  <CodeBlock>{readerAnswer}</CodeBlock>\\n  <Heading level={2}>Sheet Answer (Spreadsheet)</Heading>\\n  <CodeBlock>{JSON.stringify(sheetAnswer, null, 2)}</CodeBlock>\\n</Stack>);\"}\n\n### 124 llm_progress delegate:system-files/